{"tid":1510261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入境事務處 ： 近年來移民香港計劃","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:21:51.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cd438dfe7af0307d12bb3331e43a35a82c5ebf","tid":1510261,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"慷他人之概，最不要得。<br />\n然言，政府經常專做慷市民之概。<br />\n<br />\n例如港英的第一收容港，到現在政府成日支持難民，讓大量難民以酷刑聲請尋求政治疪護，令南亞移民倍增。又搞所謂的家庭團聚移民。<br />\n<br />\n香港人叫極政府停，政府始終都肯停呢些移民申請。<br />\n<br />\n創科局又搞科技專才移民計劃。<br />\n<br />\n官員實行要逼爆香港，令香港樓價暴升，市民百上加升。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，還要加多樣：慷他人之概最不道德，香港已無法再容納更多人口，請入境處立即停止所有移民申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2F&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=30d5b326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/</a>"},{"pid":"a9ccb20d870b7aec28cb0a4b87e172d3a8d82b80","tid":1510261,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=ea29b023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=8329e58f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3